&lt;p&gt;an exciting opportunity to be part of a newly commissioned service to improve children&#39;s management of long term respiratory conditions.. especially asthma&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a professional, motivated children&#39;s nurse with recent acute paediatrics experience and hold an additional respiratory qualification. There will be an expectation to work with primary and secondary care colleagues&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will support your development and be ked by a Lead Paediatric Respiratory Nurse Specialist and Head of Nursing.&lt;/p&gt;
